text: Oliver Batchelor (born 2 October 1996) is an English cricketer. He made his first-class debut on 26 March 2019, for Leeds/Bradford MCCU against Derbyshire, as part of the Marylebone Cricket Club University fixtures. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Leeds/Bradford MCCU cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
